 <body>
  <p>Once the content of your email is ready, you can preview it. The preview mode offers different views of the email: web and mobile versions.</p> 
  <p>To perform and inbox rendering using Litmus, refer to <a href="../../sending/using/email-rendering.md">this document</a>.</p> 
  <img alt="" captionBottom="" imageRotate="0" src="assets/email_designer_preview.png" title="" />
  <ol>
   <li><p>Select <strong>Preview</strong> to access the preview mode of the content.</p> </li>
   <li><p>Select a test profile if you want to test the personalization and dynamic content display.</p> <p>Dynamic content fragments are highlighted in orange.</p> </li>
   <li><p>To exit the <strong>Preview</strong> mode, select <strong>Edit</strong> in the top bar of the editor.</p> </li>
  </ol>
